channel.title: Custom items help goes to model requests/help section
channel.description:
There's been a few too many topics in here about custom model adding and errors with adding custom items etc. So anything model related, that includes the new whip for example, go to [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,148.0.html]Model Requests/Help[/url] section.
Thanks.
